  "texts": [
    "Nadeau et al. [124] described 60 works, Goyal et al.",
    "[63] described 48 and Patil et al. [136] described 43.",
    "However, almost all the described works in these surveys are not recent.",
    "No work after 2015 was presented by Nadeau et al. [124] and Patil et al.",
    "The main aim of our survey is to cover the most recent works proposed for entity linking."
  ]
}